 My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrf1692863383119.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrf1692863383119.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrf1692863383119.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4601862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4601862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 20, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vrf1692863383119.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vrf1692863383119.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vrf1692863383119.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vrf1692863383119\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can comment and uncomment codes in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup\n\t\tmenu.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You need to right-click on a code and click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comment</span> on the popup menu to\n\t\t\tcomment out a line when there is no selection or a complete selection of codes.\n\t\t\tSimilarly, you need to right-click inside the commented code or a selection and click\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uncomment</span> to remove a comment from the code and make the code\n\t\t\tpart of the program flow.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">The Uniface IDE editor supports the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comment</span> and\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uncomment</span> feature with the following types of codes: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__ul_qkk_ckl_4yb\">\n<li class=\"li\">ProcScript</li>\n<li class=\"li\">JavaScript in ProcScript</li>\n<li class=\"li\">JavaScript in HTML</li>\n<li class=\"li\"> CSS</li>\n<li class=\"li\"> HTML</li>\n</ul>Additionally, you can use the default shortcut keys defined for\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comment</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uncomment</span> feature in the\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">[userkeys]</code> section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file. The\n\t\t\tdefault shortcut keys defined in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">usys.ini</span> file are\n\t\t\t\t<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+K</kbd> to comment out a code and\n\t\t\t\t<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+K</kbd> to uncomment a code as defined in the following\n\t\t\tblock:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_ol2_ykh_pyb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[USERKEYS]\ncode.comment=Ctrl+K\ncode.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__note_nrl_hll_4yb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You can change the default key combinations defined in the\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">usys.ini</span> file as per your preference.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__section_swl_bpl_4yb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1201001e115\">Examples</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Comment in ProcScript</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">When the <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code> keyword is commented out, the subsequent code is treated\n\t\t\t\tas <code class=\"ph codeph\">ProcScript</code>. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">ProcScript</code> comment\n\t\t\t\t\tcharacter<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code> is used when this code is commented.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_kt4_krl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;javascript\n;  function myFunction(p1, p2) {\n;    return p1 * p2;\n;  }\n;endjavascript</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Comment in JavaScript inside ProcScript</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The code within the <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">endjavaScript</code> keywords is\n\t\t\t\ttreated as <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code>. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code> comment\n\t\t\t\tcharacters // are used when this code is commented.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_qtg_vpl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">javascript\n// function myFunction(p1, p2) {\n// return p1 * p2;\n// }\nendjavascript</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Comment in JavaScript inside HTML</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The code within the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;script&gt;</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/script&gt;</code> tags is\n\t\t\t\ttreated as <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code>. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">JavaScript</code> comment\n\t\t\t\tcharacters // are used when this code is commented.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_wtw_nrl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;sctipt&gt;\n// function myFunction(p1, p2) {\n// return p1 * p2;\n// }\n&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Comment in CSS inside HTML</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The code within the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;style&gt;</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/style&gt;</code> tags\n\t\t\t\tis treated as CSS. The CSS block comment characters <code class=\"ph codeph\">/*</code> and\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">*/</code> are used when this code is commented.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example (Single line):</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_4\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_fdh_psl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;style&gt;\n/*p.dotted {border-style: dotted;}*/\np.dashed {border-style: dashed;}\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For example (Multiple lines):</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_5\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_mvs_xsl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;style&gt;\n/*p.dotted {border-style: dotted;}\np.dashed {border-style: dashed;}*/\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Comment in HTML</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The code within the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;html&gt;</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/html&gt;</code> tags is treated\n\t\t\t\tas HTML. The HTML block comment characters <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!--</code> and\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">--&gt;</code> are used when this code is commented. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example (Single line):</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_6\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_xpw_dyl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;head&gt;\n&lt;!-- &lt;meta name=\"default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" /&gt;--&gt;\n&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" /&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For example (Multiple lines):</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vrf1692863383119_html_7\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__codeblock_ypw_dyl_4yb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;head&gt;\n&lt;!-- &lt;meta name=\"default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" /&gt;\n&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" /&gt;--&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__note_ajm_52m_4yb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Adding a comment inside a comment in HTML is not\n\t\t\t\tallowed.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"vrf1692863383119__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Block Comments</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"vrf1692863383119__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/showcase/10552636/video/893349299\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Click to watch or listen Block Comments video\" class=\"image\" id=\"vrf1692863383119__image_qyq_fqw_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4601862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4601862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Comment and uncomment code Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 20, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 You can comment and uncomment codes in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu. You need to right-click on a code and click Comment on the popup menu to comment out a line when there is no selection or a complete selection of codes. Similarly, you need to right-click inside the commented code or a selection and click Uncomment to remove a comment from the code and make the code part of the program flow. The Uniface IDE editor supports the Comment and Uncomment feature with the following types of codes: ProcScript JavaScript in ProcScript JavaScript in HTML CSS HTML Additionally, you can use the default shortcut keys defined for Comment and Uncomment feature in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file. The default shortcut keys defined in the usys.ini file are Ctrl+K to comment out a code and Ctrl+Shift+K to uncomment a code as defined in the following block: Explain this code [USERKEYS] code.comment=Ctrl+K code.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K Copy Note: You can change the default key combinations defined in the usys.ini file as per your preference. Examples Comment in ProcScript When the JavaScript keyword is commented out, the subsequent code is treated as ProcScript . The ProcScript comment character ; is used when this code is commented. For example: Explain this code ;javascript ; function myFunction(p1, p2) { ; return p1 * p2; ; } ;endjavascript Copy Comment in JavaScript inside ProcScript The code within the JavaScript and endjavaScript keywords is treated as JavaScript . The JavaScript comment characters // are used when this code is commented. For example: Explain this code javascript // function myFunction(p1, p2) { // return p1 * p2; // } endjavascript Copy Comment in JavaScript inside HTML The code within the <script> and </script> tags is treated as JavaScript . The JavaScript comment characters // are used when this code is commented. For example: Explain this code <sctipt> // function myFunction(p1, p2) { // return p1 * p2; // } </script> Copy Comment in CSS inside HTML The code within the <style> and </style> tags is treated as CSS. The CSS block comment characters /* and */ are used when this code is commented. For example (Single line): Explain this code <style> /*p.dotted {border-style: dotted;}*/ p.dashed {border-style: dashed;} </style> Copy For example (Multiple lines): Explain this code <style> /*p.dotted {border-style: dotted;} p.dashed {border-style: dashed;}*/ </style> Copy Comment in HTML The code within the <html> and </html> tags is treated as HTML. The HTML block comment characters <!-- and --> are used when this code is commented. For example (Single line): Explain this code <head> <!-- <meta name=\"default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" />--> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" /> </head> Copy For example (Multiple lines): Explain this code <head> <!-- <meta name=\"default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" /> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" />--> </head> Copy Note: Adding a comment inside a comment in HTML is not allowed. Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Block Comments Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}